{"lastModified":null,"uri":"c::10819594065::vessel::4d5ff280-0b32-11f1-b28b-8732ed1e1708","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Sardinia & Corsica\n\nLuxurious planing yacht built by Baglietto CCN, designed by DESIGN STUDIO SPADOLINI in collaboration with renowned fashion designer Roberto Cavalli, who brought his bold and elegant signature style to the vessel.\n\nPowered by three MAN V12 engines coupled with KaMeWa Rolls Royce waterjets, this yacht delivers exceptional speed, agility, and range — perfect for those who wish to cruise in absolute style without compromising on performance. Onboard comfort is outstanding, thanks to cutting-edge construction technologies and advanced automation systems that ensure intuitive, seamless, and secure yacht management.\n\nThe interiors are elegant and refined, accommodating up to six guests in welcoming, design-rich spaces finished with premium materials. The ambiance reflects Cavalli’s distinctive aesthetic. Three crew members are also comfortably accommodated.\n\nExclusive highlights on board include: a professional Sound System, a spacious and panoramic flybridge with a large sunshade — perfect for relaxing and socializing; a Williams jet tender for smooth transfers and coastal explorations; and a “Transformer” bathing platform that lowers into the water, creating a private beach club experience at the stern. A yacht that masterfully blends luxury, design, and performance for an unforgettable experience at sea.\n","blueprint":{"name":"FREEDOM","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::4d5ff280-0b32-11f1-b28b-8732ed1e1708::assets::122ff0e0-0b35-11f1-9c98-e914fd9b14ea/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::4d5ff280-0b32-11f1-b28b-8732ed1e1708::assets::122f7bb0-0b35-11f1-9c97-e914fd9b14ea/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::4d5ff280-0b32-11f1-b28b-8732ed1e1708::assets::121b0950-0b35-11f1-9c97-e914fd9b14ea/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::4d5ff280-0b32-11f1-b28b-8732ed1e170